text: Walter Parker may refer to: * Walter Richard Parker, VC (1881-1931) -- English infantryman, honoured for bravery at Gallipoli in World War I * Walter Parker (ANZAC) (1894-2000) -- Australian centenarian, one of the last three living ANZAC veterans of World War I * Walter B. Parker (1926-2014) -- American policy and transportation official in Alaska
title: Walter Parker
